OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight low cloud burning
OL,6,Fback to the coasts this morning,
OL,7,Flingering in a few places into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Otherwise dry and sunny.
OL,9,FWarm inland, locally hot across
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway, but cooler
OL,11,Falong eastern coastal districts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,14,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,15,Fthe night will remain dry with some
OL,16,Flow cloud and fog in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
