OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FDry and sunny but cloud may
OL,6,Flinger along some North Sea coastal
OL,7,Fdistricts. Warm inland, but very warm
OL,8,For hot in the southwest. Eastern
OL,9,Fcoastal areas cooler.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,12,Fdry few days with good spells of
OL,13,Fsunshine. Warm in the west with the
OL,14,Fbest of the sunshine, cloudier and
OL,15,Fcooler at times in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
